<!-- signup -->
<article class="message is-medium is-dark">
<div class="message-header has-text-centered">
<p>For Workers</p>
</div>
<div class = "message-body">
<p>If you work in the service industry, we encourage you to sign up. 
None of the information you share here is sensitive. We will just ask you for your 
name, where you worked, and your Venmo or Paypal link so that we can connect people 
who want to give you tips for years of good service already rendered.
</p>
<p><br>
If you don't have a Venmo or a PayPal you can sign up here. The process is relatively
quick and very secure. If you have any trouble both websites have decent FAQs. 
You will need to supply us with your Venmo name or the name on your PayPal.me link.
These are safe to share because without your sign-up credentials for Venmo or PayPal
neither of these can be used to take funds from your account, only to add funds to your account.</p>

<p><br>
If you have either a Venmo or a PayPal or both, you may sign up here.</p>
</div>
